eld requirements shaledrillers are designed for field safety rig up and down with pins at man level  they are fast moving and capable of walking in multiple directions the shaledriller series rigs are ac programmable energy efficient bifuel and custom designed to be best in class for the development of our clients most demanding and financially impactful exploration and development programs we excel in shale plays and other areas where completions require long horizontal sections drilling quickly and accurately to minimize open hole time and shale swelling we also excel where multiwell pads offer the option to walk between well bores and provide the opportunity to plan  hour releasetospud times unlike skidding rigs shaledrillers true multidirectional walking systems are not slowed down by misaligned wellbores and can walk over existing wellheads each independence contract drilling shaledriller rig is safe rigup  rigdown – pins at man level no use of hoists no cranes required to rig up or down fast drilling – ac programmable vfd controlled ac programmed flat screen joy stick systems provide precise control of key drilling parameters to maximize rate of penetration provide longer bit life fewer bit trips and lower well costs than mechanical or dc rigs clients drill more wells per rigyear and accelerate cash flows as wells come on line sooner than with legacy mechanical and dc rigs energy efficient bifuel and ac programming have proven to offer our clients significant fuel cost reductions in some cases up to  fast moving  site to site rig design is based on minimizing loads and reducing cycle times rig up and down does not require the use of cranes fast moving  on site all rigs can be configured to walk in multiple directions over existing wellheads – three hour release to spud times in short icd shaledriller walking rigs provide a compelling value proposition to our customers well above legacy mechanical and dc equipment and skidding ac rigs the fine control of key drilling parameters offered by shaledriller drilling systems allows sameclass wells to be drilled in half the time required by mechanical or dc equipment the combination of the shaledriller’s “safety by design” engineering process more efficient mobilization and acvfd drilling controls allows our customers to drill more wells per rig per year independence contract drilling was founded in  as a provider of premium integrated onshore drilling services shaledriller® independence contract drilling was formed in  as a premium land drilling services provider icd provides ep operators the  shaledriller series rigs read more icd shaledriller® walking rig watch video rig locations click here for a map of icds rig locations read more about us health safety  environment contract drilling investors news contact careers ethics home   independence contract drilling employeelogin click to go to the employee website independence contract drilling  employment investors news ethics careers contact home about us health safety  environment contract drilling available careers application application for employment independence contract drilling inc and each of its subsidiaries icd is an equal opportunity employer we do not discriminate on the basis of race religion national origin color sex age or disability it is our intent that all applicants be given equal opportunity with selection decisions based on jobrelated factors fields marked  are required position applied for  with  ic drilling      personal information last name  first name  middle name street address      city  state  zipcode  home phone please use numbers only  cell phone please use numbers only      email address          job information date you can start     expected pay rate per do you have the legal right to work in the united states yes no have you ever worked for icd yes no if yes please give dates and company do you have any relatives employed at icd yes no if yes please give name and relationship have you ever been