om all liability for any damages that may result from furnishing information regarding me i understand that this application does not create a contract of employment obligate icd to offer me employment or to hire me i further understand that if i am employed by icd my employment will be on at “at will” basis and may be terminated by icd at any time with or without cause or notice if i am employed i understand that i will wear all required personal protection equipment and will abide by all federal state local laws and icd procedures and regulations while working for icd in connection with my application for employment with icd i understand that investigational background inquires may be conducted on me including consumer criminal driving and industrial safety records these reports will include but no be limited to information regarding my character work habits performance and experience along with reasons for termination of employment with previous employers i acknowledge that i have been provided with a summary of my rights relating to a consumer background investigation and that i have authorized icd to conduct a consumer background investigation on me further i understand that information from various federal state and local agencies may be requested regarding my past activities relating to driving credit criminal and civil litigation as well as claims involving me in the records of insurance companies i agree to submit to medical testing including a physical examination and drug and alcohol testing i understand that failure to submit to any of these tests or an unsatisfactory result from any of these tests will disqualify me from further consideration for employment with icd please submit application to hricdrillingcom for review i have read and understand the above       yes   independence contract drilling was founded in  as a provider of premium integrated onshore drilling services   shaledriller® independence contract drilling was formed in  as a premium lan